  <ul>
    <li>Ability Score Increase: Your Intelligence score increases by 2 and your Charisma score increases by 1.</li>
    <li>Size: The Sorceron-blooded are generally similar to elves or humans in height, weight, and build. Your size is medium.</li>
    <li>Speed: Your base walking speed is 30 ft.</li>
    <li>
      Natural Spellcaster: Choose two cantrips from the wizard spell list, you can cast these cantrips at will using Intelligence as your spellcasting stat.
      Additionally choose one 1st level spell from the wizard spell list, you know that spell inherently, however, once you cast it you must complete a short rest
      before you can cast it again.
    </li>
    <li>Master of the Arcane: You have advantage on Intelligence (Arcana) and Intelligence (History) checks.</li>
  </ul>
